      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Shhmashhana kalika. The dark-bodied Goddess of the cremation ground, the power of death and dissolution. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 2,
      "source_index": 2,
      "post_id": "814766726962118656",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766726962118656",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:15:01.582675+00:00",
      "text_hash": "90dafb2182fbd7d875f0bc544727473dc83288263a52fe2801bc6ed25af94abd",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kali. The Black Goddess, ruler of Time. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 3,
      "source_index": 3,
      "post_id": "814766799712305152",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766799712305152",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:16:11.005279+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b11201e902877922dd084a61eaaa953f1caa5183e18545a1ba0a8b9b5c379286",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Bhadra kali. The all-auspicious Dark Mother. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 4,
      "source_index": 4,
      "post_id": "814766947836248064",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766947836248064",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:18:32.187080+00:00",
      "text_hash": "56d5fd427fc92382364dd0098195c515517609c2fdeabecb96539991031578ea",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kapalini. She who bears the skull, showing Her transcendence over mortality and the cycle of creation. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 5,
      "source_index": 5,
      "post_id": "814770374806061056",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814770374806061056",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T10:13:00.415367+00:00",
      "text_hash": "95e4ee6dc2d77f343c485f9688fc36b5e7f765a161282673e1f69c979e88903c",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Guhya kali. The hidden and secret Dark Goddess. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 6,
      "source_index": 6,
      "post_id": "814772529677877248",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814772529677877248",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T10:47:15.522075+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b8b796e6c9e28373b7824ce6abecb9b04bce7271ac4dc1afa9838aa338f47ca8",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Maha-kali. The Great Dark Mother, beautiful and compassionate to devotees, yet terrifying to their enemies. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 7,
      "source_index": 7,
      "post_id": "814775871450824704",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814775871450824704",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T11:40:22.404418+00:00",
      "text_hash": "f18872c50d3f400a39222ae4444547c8a15ed051cf15b3fb0610d5a0c0e87570",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kurukulla-'virodhini. The destroyer of opposition, especially as the one who bestows siddhis and protects those who attain them. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 8,
      "source_index": 8,
      "post_id": "814777384819736576",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814777384819736576",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T12:04:25.702749+00:00",
      "text_hash": "ef6dbbc4e80fac6e5c61a8129d9202f820a812e7e7bbdecd8ea2c068b5ff2344",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalika. The tender form of Kali, the Dark One, gentle in presence yet potent in power. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 9,
      "source_index": 9,
      "post_id": "814779595930927104",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814779595930927104",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T12:39:34.364154+00:00",
      "text_hash": "14da8638e51cc428a80279b454a7482965617e551173fd2e0642aeb08cecfbb1",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala ratri cha. She who is the Dark Night of Time, the profound dissolution and ultimate reality beyond all manifestations. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 10,
      "source_index": 10,
      "post_id": "814781608631631872",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814781608631631872",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T13:11:33.918244+00:00",
      "text_hash": "ea7dd2778070f5dd4d436a617a8e5ed9d758f7714a814d0435fa6cc320167a1d",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Maha-kala nitambini. The dark-limbed one who rests upon Mahakala, the great Lord of Time. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 11,
      "source_index": 11,
      "post_id": "814784310832939008",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814784310832939008",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T13:54:30.973948+00:00",
      "text_hash": "661a438d5bbe47e04346645b6524ed582056cfed9ff79736a19a6eaf124ba056",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala bhairava bharya cha. The consort of Kala Bhairava. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 12,
      "source_index": 12,
      "post_id": "814787762461032448",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814787762461032448",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T14:49:22.643002+00:00",
      "text_hash": "9724f38341ede114319703792acc5a9168db68cce81a0fcdd47bd11f77d33ede",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kula vartma prakashhini. The illuminator of the path of the spiritual lineage, revealing the essence of the Kaula tradition. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 13,
      "source_index": 13,
      "post_id": "814791128198070273",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814791128198070273",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T15:42:52.731458+00:00",
      "text_hash": "df91bbe7bc1ef7e6242bab2cd18cc2b319190581f46e9a054740323d5b5116ca",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamada. The fulfiller of all desires. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 14,
      "source_index": 14,
      "post_id": "814792823235837952",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814792823235837952",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T16:09:48.922942+00:00",
      "text_hash": "1d533cd98dd70f1627aaef1c915d48684392831e075233f67df3e495bbf87a8a",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamini. The beautiful and desirable Goddess, the object of divine love and devotion. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 15,
      "source_index": 15,
      "post_id": "814794452577222656",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814794452577222656",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T16:35:42.809739+00:00",
      "text_hash": "f03db160bfd8aaccb62d2f4e8474068e3994c77b9a95222c4730604a7e9b34b6",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamya. She who embodies all longing and aspiration. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 16,
      "source_index": 16,
      "post_id": "814796532572438529",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814796532572438529",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T17:08:46.720187+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b8195aa80484d70fba3ac35f3c5a336748f810deb97c765d1a3ebecef4577ae3",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamaniya swa-bhavini. She whose very nature is beauty and loveliness. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 17,
      "source_index": 17,
      "post_id": "814798180972740608",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814798180972740608",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T17:34:58.520927+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b0aaabc4c4c2d6e9357e4aefd5c78ca18c91f13f131c5edca88a72fd9c61ca39",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kasturi rasa liptanggi. Her body is anointed with the essence of musk. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 18,
      "source_index": 18,
      "post_id": "814799845798936576",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814799845798936576",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T18:01:26.124404+00:00",
      "text_hash": "42d56f57fb309e987bcb9d32b7fe5c1578af7ca33626c3b7d69c24ed509325a5",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kunjar'eshhwara gamini. She who moves with the majestic gait of the Lord of Elephants, embodying power and grace. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 19,
      "source_index": 19,
      "post_id": "814801749204434944",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814801749204434944",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T18:31:41.488532+00:00",
      "text_hash": "9f5e5952d5ef0369f7f87b4e98b05c3c9a84c356b8772df245517405dda3d0dd",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kakara varna sarv'anggi. She whose entire body bears the color of the letter Ka, signifying Time and ultimate reality. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 20,
      "source_index": 20,
      "post_id": "814804010531979264",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814804010531979264",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T19:07:37.995776+00:00",
      "text_hash": "cfcbfb8b25e18743d93d216e856e07aaaffea8552ed5aa39b754e5d057ff7f49",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamini kama sundari. The beautiful One who awakens desire in Kama, the God of Love, and who is Herself the embodiment of all desires. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 21,
      "source_index": 21,
      "post_id": "814805806249852928",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814805806249852928",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T19:36:10.526338+00:00",
      "text_hash": "4828df0105e71c120cf9a928c3e07b346eb625bb6f0978064c3312dd415ccf7e",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kamarta. The passionate One, ablaze with divine desire to destroy evil. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 22,
      "source_index": 22,
      "post_id": "814807438788263936",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814807438788263936",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T20:02:07.414559+00:00",
      "text_hash": "dd15744b4461b8d93efc46f9349f21380244a7b7be05f2fb468903fe23fea27a",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kama rupacha. She who can assume any form at will for the protection of devotees or the destruction of evil. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 23,
      "source_index": 23,
      "post_id": "814809278392270848",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814809278392270848",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T20:31:21.969075+00:00",
      "text_hash": "8bfae60fc537fab9b53d14e10f182b55cc8719ba5e02f4d1f2a14e068de445ec",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kama dhenu. The wish-fulfilling Cow, bestowing every aspiration. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 24,
      "source_index": 24,
      "post_id": "814811353656213504",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814811353656213504",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T21:04:20.883138+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b0d10ce6b19bf67c8d2dbb89f9f7c85ad770648537ca2fc71a8fe7e17a23f692",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala-vati. She who embodies all kalas, the portions or phases of the Moon. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 25,
      "source_index": 25,
      "post_id": "814813163634737152",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814813163634737152",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T21:33:07.036688+00:00",
      "text_hash": "a6a2a9e02c1b8a57ec1960a60c38646d3dd569a2566f74f74343091aa233eefd",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kanta. The Beloved One, charming and radiant. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 26,
      "source_index": 26,
      "post_id": "814815017091448833",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814815017091448833",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T22:02:34.607528+00:00",
      "text_hash": "54dbfbce8d82d4d4f567cd0de7d19d7d4af343c8837f12c534ffde27939b899b",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kama swarupa cha. The very embodiment of desire, and the granter of desires. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 27,
      "source_index": 27,
      "post_id": "814816684285329409",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814816684285329409",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T22:29:04.593599+00:00",
      "text_hash": "62419fa8a1bc2d54920b51b32028236d1914e1f7fadd86bd76ee07042f3984ef",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kam'akhya. The famed and supreme Red Goddess who abides in the Yoni seat of Assam, fulfilling desires. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 28,
      "source_index": 28,
      "post_id": "814818682063732736",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814818682063732736",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T23:00:49.803953+00:00",
      "text_hash": "6e8935aed7f71bd3bf5973be16502c2a2b36e14155212f7f222e99468e86a1e2",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kula palini. The protectress of family, tradition, and spiritual lineage. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 29,
      "source_index": 29,
      "post_id": "814820407642341376",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814820407642341376",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T23:28:15.648375+00:00",
      "text_hash": "3b8b3d7e77762e47bba4c1e31ec2cd1bc8d03958d131804244b41e16bb92120c",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kulina. She who dwells in the lineage, the Noble One. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 30,
      "source_index": 30,
      "post_id": "814822302935056384",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814822302935056384",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T23:58:22.894573+00:00",
      "text_hash": "fd17052a167fcd0c0570717956f3f8133b0f7560eed9c940b9b21c92179d1531",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kula-vaty'amba. The Mother of the Kula, the lineage of devotees. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 31,
      "source_index": 31,
      "post_id": "814826170365411328",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814826170365411328",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-25T00:59:51.205289+00:00",
      "text_hash": "4891607761187cc2dea4c4c76beceb5b8d6499cb63056c943bdf4fcf9529d426",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Durga. The inaccessible and invincible Mother, the protecting fortress. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    }
  ]
}
